---
title: Indian-Style Chickpea & Pistachio Burger with Turmeric Wedges and Rocket
description: Because of their texture, chickpeas make a great substitute for ground beef and work brilliantly alongside punchier flavours like our Zanzibar curry powder. Combined with chopped coriander, pistachios, grated carrot, and mango chutney, shaped into burger patties and fried until golden, they’re the perfect thing to make for a midweek veggie treat.
